Maori treatment
Homonym Number:
Word Class: noun
Sense Number:  1
Definition:the burning of the tops of root-crops after frost-bite in order to save a crop.


Origin: [none]
Register:
Register 2:
Flag: Farm Words
Domain: Rural
Region: [none]
